snippet.title: YOU DON'T KNOW JACK TELEVISION Trailer
snippet.description: No, this is not a video of the YDKJ TV show that aired on ABC in 2001. It's the YDKJ PC game with trivia all about TV shows! Fans of host Josh "Schmitty" Schmitstinstein will love this walk down boob-tube memory lane. If you thought all those hours of watching TV were good for nothing, then YOU DON'T KNOW JACK... Television!
